WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.708
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.708 --> 00:00:03.520
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:13.869
I'm going to just get right to it, but first off, I want to take the time to give God praise and say, 'For the Lord is good and His mercy endures forever.

00:00:13.869 --> 00:01:09.560
' Everyone needs to say that; I would say you can go through your whole day always thinking that the Lord is good and His mercy endures forever, and that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:22.754
He's the same as what He was back then; He's never changed.

00:01:22.754 --> 00:01:35.960
He is doing miracles today just like what He did 2,000 years ago.

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:40.792
You just have to believe.

00:01:40.792 --> 00:01:54.320
I believe with all my heart we are about to see signs, wonders, and creative miracles.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:02:06.711
We're going to see demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:02:17.740 --> 00:02:18.000
I want to be encouraging today.

00:02:27.751 --> 00:03:05.646
I know I've dropped some really heavy videos, and I know that that was what the Holy Spirit told me to do, but I felt today the Lord told me to try to lift you all up and get you excited.

00:03:05.646 --> 00:03:16.160
Let you know that the sky is not falling.

00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:26.528
Things aren't all getting bad for the body of Christ.

00:03:26.528 --> 00:03:49.511
When things are getting darker for the world, the light is going to get lighter for the body of Christ.

00:03:56.549 --> 00:04:06.799
I've said it before and I'll say it again: it's like a quarter with two sides.

00:04:16.700 --> 00:04:20.529
The dark is going to get darker, and the light is going to get lighter.

00:04:20.529 --> 00:04:27.900
Which side do you want to focus on?

00:04:27.900 --> 00:04:52.575
What you put your attention on the most is what's going to get bigger in your life, and I'm going to focus on the glory.

00:04:52.575 --> 00:05:39.435
Yes, I have to tell you what the Holy Spirit tells me, but on the other side of it, there is a great outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord coming to this earth in a way we've never seen before.

00:05:52.039 --> 00:05:57.465
It's going to be a glorious outpouring, a move like we've never seen before.

00:05:57.465 --> 00:06:05.968
He said, 'Behold, I do a new thing.

00:06:05.968 --> 00:06:23.720
' He's going to bring forth water in the desert; it's going to be amazing.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:45.880
I remember when I was driving down the road and the Lord said, 'There's very sobering days coming, Brandon.

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:56.258
' But then He asked, 'What's the opposite of being sober?

00:06:56.258 --> 00:07:01.639
' I said, 'Well, Lord, being drunk.

00:07:01.639 --> 00:07:08.818
' He said, 'That's right.

00:07:08.818 --> 00:07:30.071
Be filled with the Holy Spirit; be drunk in the Holy Ghost, stirred up in your spirit, and filled to overflowing.

00:07:30.071 --> 00:07:39.484
' Out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:07:46.640 --> 00:08:37.050
The Lord told me that you're going to have to learn how to live in a state of being filled with the Spirit of the Lord in these last days, stirring yourself up in your most holy faith by praying in the Holy Ghost.

00:08:37.050 --> 00:08:49.166
I believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost.

00:08:49.166 --> 00:09:19.279
I know there are Baptists, Methodists, Catholics, and all kinds of people on here, but I'm charismatic and I believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost.

00:09:19.279 --> 00:10:02.750
I unashamedly believe with all my heart that you have the ability to pray in tongues, and according to Acts chapter 2, that is still going on today.

00:10:02.750 --> 00:10:18.819
We can pray in an unknown tongue to the Father and pray mysteries to the Lord.

00:10:18.819 --> 00:10:36.415
It's like your secret language to the Lord that the devil doesn't understand.

00:10:43.543 --> 00:10:59.947
When you're praying in English, he hears you and thinks he's getting to you because you're whining about your flesh.

00:10:59.947 --> 00:11:13.095
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:11:13.095 --> 00:11:32.280
Sometimes I don't want him to hear what I'm saying, so I pray in tongues.

00:11:37.799 --> 00:11:51.330
It bypasses my flesh and my intellect and goes straight to the Lord's throne room.

00:11:59.839 --> 00:12:12.854
If you want to be baptized in the Holy Spirit, today could be your day.

00:12:12.854 --> 00:12:46.490
I believe for you to receive a fresh touch and a fresh fire of the Holy Spirit on your life, and that you'll speak in other tongues and walk in the supernatural.

00:12:46.490 --> 00:13:12.444
People want to know how to walk in the supernatural or have visitations and demonstrations of angelic visitations and Jesus coming.

00:13:12.444 --> 00:13:20.244
I've had eight visitations from Jesus.

00:13:20.244 --> 00:13:41.680
I'm not anything special, but I make an atmosphere for Him to want to visit.

00:13:41.680 --> 00:13:45.404
He inhabits the praises of His people.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:14:10.226
If you make a place for the Holy Spirit to be comfortable in your home, car, or workplace, He'll come and visit.

00:14:10.226 --> 00:14:17.812
It's about practicing His presence.

00:14:17.812 --> 00:14:22.090
I don't act religious.

00:14:22.090 --> 00:14:46.355
I've learned, even more so in the last couple of days, how many people are a bunch of Pharisees in this comment section.

00:14:46.355 --> 00:15:27.218
I was asking the Lord what was going on with these comments, and He said, 'Brandon, there is a lot of satanic agenda whenever you get broadcasted all over the world.

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:47.547
There are people that have been assigned to try to cause havoc in the comment section and cause division and strife.

00:15:47.547 --> 00:15:56.800
' They're planted there, so just pray and bless them.

00:15:59.240 --> 00:16:14.030
I'm going to walk in love; perfect love casts out all fear.

00:16:14.620 --> 00:16:25.272
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:16:37.500 --> 00:16:45.467
I bless every one of you trolls out there, but I'll just hide you, block you, or shadowban you.

00:16:45.467 --> 00:17:15.765
The Lord's got this, and I'm excited because people are getting born again on this channel and set free by the power of Jesus' name.

00:17:15.765 --> 00:17:32.354
I talked to someone yesterday who asked why some people don't get healed when we pray.

00:17:39.627 --> 00:17:51.028
You will never walk totally in the supernatural without a foundation of the Word of God.

00:17:51.028 --> 00:18:19.222
You have to make the Word a priority; it is beyond any prophetic word you will hear on YouTube.

00:18:19.222 --> 00:18:33.560
The Word of God stands alone as the foundation in your life.

00:18:33.560 --> 00:18:48.053
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by the Word of God.

00:18:48.053 --> 00:19:20.914
If you don't get that Word down inside of you, you can be snared by familiar spirits and demonic stuff that comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:19:20.914 --> 00:19:41.070
He comes as an angel of light, not a devil with horns and a pitchfork.

00:19:44.240 --> 00:19:54.328
He is subtle, like the serpent that spoke in Eve's ear.

00:19:54.328 --> 00:20:10.159
When you are laying hands on the sick, why don't we see miracles more often?

00:20:10.909 --> 00:20:42.725
The Bible says, 'If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, ye shall ask what ye will, and it shall be done for you.

00:20:42.725 --> 00:20:50.840
' Let's check our Word level.

00:20:58.173 --> 00:21:24.590
You have to have a revelation and a manifestation of that rhema word to get the manifestation of what you're believing for.

00:21:24.590 --> 00:21:42.480
If your Word level is low and you're not seeing miracles, that's why.

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:51.143
The Word is the only thing that delivers.

00:21:53.924 --> 00:22:07.160
He sent His Word to set the captives free.

00:22:07.160 --> 00:22:32.060
We are set free by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

00:22:32.060 --> 00:22:48.520
Everything we will ever need is found in the Word of God.

00:22:59.1000 --> 00:23:09.400
If you don't have a scripture for what you're believing for—finances, healing, or your marriage—find it.

00:23:09.400 --> 00:23:28.570
Use a Bible app to search for scriptures on overcoming depression or addictions and start meditating on them.

00:23:28.570 --> 00:23:31.290
Renew your mind.

00:23:31.290 --> 00:23:52.404
When that Word gets down inside your spirit like a deep root, it will cultivate and spring forth good fruit.

00:23:52.404 --> 00:24:04.177
Then you lay hands on the sick, and they will recover.

00:24:04.177 --> 00:24:25.939
But if you're doing it out of an empty Word base, you won't see results.

00:24:25.939 --> 00:25:15.411
When I prayed for my dogs and they were raised from the dead, or when I laid hands on the man who got brand new lungs, I was meditating on the Word on a continual basis.

00:25:32.293 --> 00:25:34.644
You have to feed your spirit just like you feed your flesh.

00:25:34.644 --> 00:26:07.884
Many people only feed their spirit on Sundays, but you should feed your spirit breakfast, lunch, and dinner to keep it strong.

00:26:07.884 --> 00:26:27.679
You need a relationship with the Lord in good times and in bad.

00:26:28.834 --> 00:26:44.053
You wouldn't only talk to your spouse when you wanted something.

00:26:44.053 --> 00:26:59.855
Getting that Word inside you is easy; you just have to be determined.

00:26:59.855 --> 00:27:07.120
Faith works by love.

00:27:07.120 --> 00:27:20.090
If your faith isn't working, check your love walk.

00:27:20.090 --> 00:27:32.875
They go together because God is love and God is the Word.

00:27:35.640 --> 00:28:01.904
The angels once told me that the most important thing we will be judged on in heaven is how we handled love.

00:28:01.904 --> 00:28:12.406
Love is the key to the glory.

00:28:13.382 --> 00:28:26.260
The glorious outpouring is attached to the love of God.

00:28:26.260 --> 00:28:46.485
If you are in strife or discord in your home, check your love tank.

00:28:46.485 --> 00:28:51.457
Love never fails.

00:28:51.457 --> 00:29:07.017
Sometimes I feel dry and the Lord tells me, 'Brandon, your Word level's low.

00:29:12.088 --> 00:29:14.754
You haven't been in the Word enough.

00:29:14.754 --> 00:29:42.720
' You've got to fill yourself with the Holy Ghost, pray in the spirit, and jump in that river.

00:29:43.260 --> 00:30:11.439
I have the same Holy Spirit inside of me as you do; I just choose to operate in it more.

00:30:11.439 --> 00:30:29.543
He is no respecter of persons, but He is a respecter of faith.

00:30:29.543 --> 00:30:47.089
If you aren't seeing miracles, it's because you're ignorant of the Word.

00:31:00.557 --> 00:31:04.120
The Bible says that by His stripes we are healed.

00:31:04.120 --> 00:31:50.200
When the evening was come, they brought Him many who were possessed, and He cast out the spirits with His word and healed all who were oppressed.

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:57.630
Do you believe Jesus will do it for you?

00:31:57.630 --> 00:32:00.662
Most people believe He can, but do you believe He has compassion on you?

00:33:01.491 --> 00:33:09.375
The woman with the issue of blood believed it, and her faith made her whole.

00:33:27.233 --> 00:33:35.045
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:33:35.045 --> 00:34:05.474
We receive salvation by grace through faith, and it takes the same amount of faith to believe for healing.

00:34:05.780 --> 00:34:38.000
You have to be like a bulldog on a bone; I'm not letting go of what He promised me.

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:49.969
Father, I thank you for every person represented here.

00:35:18.068 --> 00:35:21.287
I call healing over their bodies right now in the name of Jesus.

00:35:21.556 --> 00:35:35.529
I command sickness and the foul devil of infirmity to let them go.

00:35:35.529 --> 00:35:48.466
We call them delivered by the blood of Jesus.

00:35:57.400 --> 00:36:09.280
I call their minds free from the spirit of fear and PTSD.

00:36:09.280 --> 00:36:40.080
I pray peace over their minds and call those memories of tragic events off of them.

00:37:10.295 --> 00:37:38.400
I speak life over their adrenal glands and cortisol levels; adrenal fatigue is wiped out.

00:38:11.133 --> 00:38:11.547
I call healing from cancers and tumors.

00:38:11.547 --> 00:38:38.135
We say in the name of Jesus they are delivered from diabetes, indigestion, and acid reflux.

00:38:38.135 --> 00:39:46.235
I speak to cataracts: go now in the name of Jesus.

00:39:46.235 --> 00:40:52.365
I call ears to pop open and hearing to be restored.

00:41:18.031 --> 00:41:50.750
I speak to tennis elbow, arthritis, and plantar fasciitis to go now.

00:42:09.724 --> 00:42:14.800
I call blood disorders like HIV and hepatitis healed.

00:42:35.085 --> 00:42:40.775
I bind every foul devil associated with blood disorders and command you to leave.

00:42:40.775 --> 00:43:08.510
Receive the fire of the Holy Spirit to burn out growths and tumors.

00:43:08.510 --> 00:43:26.775
I speak to that man's prostate: be healed and whole.

00:43:33.880 --> 00:43:51.387
I call restoration over female organs and the seed of man.

00:43:51.387 --> 00:44:13.816
You will conceive and receive a baby; you will not miscarry this time.

00:44:13.816 --> 00:44:22.800
It will be a full-term pregnancy.

00:44:39.493 --> 00:45:26.650
The Lord said He's going to bless your womb.

00:45:26.650 --> 00:45:44.904
Renew your mind with the Word.

00:45:44.904 --> 00:45:55.142
Thank you, Lord, for demonstrations and manifestations.

00:45:55.142 --> 00:46:05.829
We're not under the curse; Jesus has set us free.

00:46:37.333 --> 00:46:58.347
For sickness I have health, for poverty wealth, for Christ has ransomed me.

00:47:01.750 --> 00:47:39.566
In His presence, troubles vanish and hearts are mended.

00:47:39.566 --> 00:48:49.520
Reach out and grab it by faith.

00:48:49.520 --> 00:49:31.320
His name is Jesus; rise and be healed.

00:49:44.359 --> 00:49:46.440
Receive the power of the Holy Spirit now.

00:49:50.480 --> 00:49:55.232
I hope this blessed you.

00:50:17.520 --> 00:50:17.760
I had a fresh touch myself.

00:50:17.760 --> 00:50:22.370
Remember, Jesus loves you.

00:50:43.186 --> 00:50:44.226
God bless you.
